				\begin{document}$$Cu_{Sn}^{2 - }$$\end{document}) are the dominant defects, especially for n-type CsSnBr3, in which it serves as an acceptor. When the host is under the hole-rich conditions (p-type), a significant amount of interstitial impurities (Aui+\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
